                                InitPrinter


    InitPrinter initializes your printer with the print options specified
in the Printer and PrinterGFX editors. To initialize your Printer, first
turn it on then double-click on the InitPrinter icon. When you turn your
printer off it doesn't retain the print options, and so has to be
reinitialized with InitPrinter when you turn it on again.


